{
  "stem": "26731.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I couldn't figure out then and can't figure out now how the men got there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The tension wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Not he was overly friendly, but there was not the tension.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was correct, not friendly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But for some reason, you could feel he didn't want to harass you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He would, actually-- wanted to make it easy on you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was-- absolutely not one-- never raised his voice, not one improper word, anything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The man, to me-- for some reason, he actually liked me, put me to work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Do this and that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when he came, he seemed genuinely concerned.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't know what the man was doing there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Obviously, he didn't belong there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I sometimes wonder, probably a young man got there, he couldn't help himself.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He couldn't get out of it, I wonder.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Apparently, he was an officer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had that SD, [GERMAN], 'security service,' right on his sleeve.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was there with the others.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he was the one guy who, for some reason, if I would meet him now, I would invite him to sit down with me.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] To me and others, he did not one intemperate word, not one remark or anything else.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Very-- [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, it was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You never knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You never knew what those-- Gunther.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Who knows, he might get the idea to-- what, maybe you did something wrong that he disliked.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You never knew with those guys.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe he knew that he was-- and that there wasn't a permanent crew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't do what he did actually there-- only Jews there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's the reason after the war, [INAUDIBLE] I had enough.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said, no, things have died down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They did-- actually don't know me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I wasn't actually-- didn't have to check in by name.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
